http://www.charbroil.com/multi-purpose-cooker.html

The Multi-Purpose Cooker from Char-Broil

OVERVIEW   
• 34,000 BTU porcelain coated steel tube burner
• Two independently-controlled burner rings elimate cold spots
• 165 sq. inch (17" dia) stainless paella pan with hi-temp red painted handles
• Fits small (16") up to large (22") paella pans
• Sturdy painted tripod provides a stable base
• No tools required for assembly

SPECS
    • Dimensions Assembled (in inches) - 34 x 34 x 32.75
    • Primary Burner BTU's - 34,000
    • Primary Cooking Surface (sq. in.) - 165
    • Natural Gas Convertible - No
    • Fuel Source - Propane
    • Carton Size (in inches) - 31.5 x 17.6 x 8.3
    • Grilling Surface Height (in inches) - 32.8
